1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:05,172
When you start the activities, they will follow the same order as this lesson.

2
00:00:05,122 --> 00:00:13,260
First, you do a warm-up: Staff will ask you to move slowly to top-left, top-right, bottom-left and bottom-right.

3
00:00:13,260 --> 00:00:15,896
Repeat until movement is calmer.

4
00:00:15,896 --> 00:00:20,475
Then you answer quick checks, so we know the key words make sense.

5
00:00:20,475 --> 00:00:27,282
Next, you practise the real computer skill: Use real icons or safe blank desktop space.

6
00:00:27,282 --> 00:00:32,038
Staff will name a target, You moves to it and single-clicks once.

7
00:00:32,038 --> 00:00:37,160
You may also type a short answer, for example: Type the word click.

8
00:00:37,160 --> 00:00:44,035
At the end, you finish with a stretch or reflection: Staff will say the target name but avoids pointing.

9
00:00:44,035 --> 00:00:47,703
Move back to gesture prompts only if you gets stuck.

10
00:00:47,703 --> 00:00:50,254
Take one activity at a time.

11
00:00:50,254 --> 00:00:54,796
If you need help, ask staff, then try the next step yourself.

